data.title: Fresh and Delicious!
data.text: Absolutely yummy! Nice little cafe inside the Regions Bank building. Plenty of seats and very cute. The staff is very responsive. I had the buffalo chicken wrap and the banana berry smoothie-so tasty. I have gone back twice just for the smoothie as a treat in the afternoon. I would highly recommend this yummy place.

data.title: Best Smoothie
data.text: I love this place for their smoothies - the Kale and Spinach is amazing - I love it.  Breakfast is great too and their salads and sandwiches are awesome too

data.title: Great, wholesome food.
data.text: I always enjoyed visits to Nature's Table.  It was close to my office, and located right under a large office building.  The food was always fresh and great.  I knocked off one point because every time I'm there it always seems terribly disorganized, but the staff are nice enough that it is never a real problem.

data.title: just right
data.text: Their servings were just right for a quick lunch on the go.  I ate here a couple times during my stay there.
